  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>announcements</td>
    <td>公告通知</td>
    <td>title, content, isTop, category</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>user_preferences</td>
    <td>用户偏好</td>
    <td>预定偏好、搜索历史</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>trip_templates</td>
    <td>出差模板</td>
    <td>目的地、费用模板</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>holiday_configs</td>
    <td>节假日配置</td>
    <td>date, name, isWorkday</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>document_view_logs</td>
    <td>文档浏览记录</td>
    <td>userId, documentId, viewedAt</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>search_histories</td>
    <td>搜索历史</td>
    <td>userId, keyword</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h2>6.2 核心数据关系</h2>
<pre>
users (1) ──── (N) reservations
users (1) ──── (N) trips
users (1) ──── (N) leaves
users (1) ──── (N) attendances
users (1) ──── (N) todos
users (1) ──── (N) document_view_logs

meeting_rooms (1) ──── (N) reservations

documents (N) ──── (1) document_categories
</pre>

